Package: xpdf
Version: 3.01
Revision: 2
GCC: 3.3
Source: ftp://www.foolabs.com/pub/%n/%n-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: e004c69c7dddef165d768b1362b44268
Depends: x11, ghostscript-fonts, t1lib1-shlibs, openmotif3-shlibs, libpaper1-shlibs
